                def __init__(self):
                    self._attr = None

                def getter(self):
                    print("Got attribute")

                    print("Setting attribute")
                    self._attr = value * 2
                    print("Attribute set")

            obj.attr = 2345
            print("obj.attr =", obj.attr)

            try:
                del obj.attr
                print("Shouldn't be able to delete attribute.")
            except AttributeError:
                print("Couldn't delete attribute.")

            print("Done.")
